{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b5a7ffc696","title":"对观察家评论稿《联合国往哪里去？》的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ab730b431","index":0,"year":1965,"month":2,"day":14,"articleId":"b5a7ffc696"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9beeb46262","type":"title","text":"对观察家评论稿《联合国往哪里去？》的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696"},{"id":"52e898fca1","type":"paragraph","text":"写得很好，照此发表。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696"},{"id":"fec3ccf18d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696"},{"id":"a53d289072","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696"},{"id":"7f214fd299","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这个批语写在周恩来1965年2月14日送审的拟在《人民日报》刊登的观察家评论稿《联合国往哪里去？——评戴高乐的讲话》上。评论说，对于联合国的现状，世界上多数国家是不满意的。法国总统戴高乐2月4日在记者招待会上批评联合国的讲话表明，即使在北大西洋集团内部，也有人认为联合国作为美国家天下的局面应该结束了。现在，从东方到西方，要求彻底改组联合国的呼声越来越高，各种各样的方案已经提了出来。不管哪种方案，一个共同之点，就是要求结束美国把持和操纵联合国的局面。联合国必须改正错误，彻底改组，已经成为当前人心之所向、大势之所趟。这篇文章在1965年2月15日《人民日报》发表。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696"}],"page":{"id":"bdd5b6bc61","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"b5a7ffc696","start":493,"end":493}}}},"__N_SSG":true}